NOTE BROADCASTER
GRAB 300
SEEK 1
COPY F M
COPY F M
SEEK -99
COPY F M
HALT

xb
LINK 800
MARK EASTWEST
COPY M X
TEST X < 0
TJMP WEST
FJMP EAST

MARK NORTHSOUTH
COPY M X
TEST X < 0
TJMP SOUTH
FJMP NORTH


MARK WEST
TEST X = 0
TJMP NORTHSOUTH
LINK 803
ADDI X 1 X
JUMP WEST
MARK EAST
TEST X = 0
TJMP NORTHSOUTH
LINK 801
ADDI X -1 X
JUMP EAST

MARK SOUTH
TEST X = 0
TJMP WRITE
LINK 802
ADDI X 1 X
JUMP SOUTH
MARK NORTH
TEST X = 0
TJMP WRITE
LINK 800
ADDI X -1 X
JUMP NORTH

MARK WRITE
COPY M X
GRAB 200
MARK SEARCH
TEST F = X
FJMP SEARCH
COPY F X
@REP 4
COPY X F
@END
